metadata.name: JANUS #1
metadata.description:
JANUS. The god of beginnings and endings. A song with many faces, taking a new shape with every new edition. Changes and transitions. From past to future, from one condition to another. Impermanence.

JANUS symbolizes the technological changes that allow for a new paradigm, where music creation becomes a shapeshifting process with endless combinations that never settles on a final form.

JANUS is a collaboration between Maelstrom & Ipno, based on DIY ethos and tools : trust the process. Embrace the accidents.

JANUS is the genesis Async Music Blueprint.
